#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.kaddressbook.appdata.xml:9
msgid "KAddressBook"
msgstr "KAddressBook"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.kaddressbook.appdata.xml:10
msgid "An address book manager"
msgstr "Helbide-liburuaren kudeatzaile bat"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kaddressbook.appdata.xml:12
msgid ""
"KAddressBook stores all the personal details of your family, friends and "
"other contacts. It supports large variety of services, including NextCloud, "
"Kolab, Google Contacts, Microsoft Exchange (EWS) or any standard CalDAV "
"server."
msgstr ""
"KAddressBook zure familiaren, lagunen eta beste kontaktu batzuen xehetasunak "
"pertsonal guztiak biltegiratzen ditu. Zerbitzu aniztasun handia onartzen du, "
"NextCloud, Kolab, Google Contacts, Microsoft Exchange (EWS) edo edozein "
"CalDAV estandar."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kaddressbook.appdata.xml:13
msgid "Features:"
msgstr "Ezaugarriak:"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kaddressbook.appdata.xml:15
msgid ""
"Powerful search - KAddressBook has configurable filters and powerful search "
"capabilities."
msgstr ""
"Bilaketa ahaltsua - KAddressBook-ek konfigura daitezkeen iragazkiak eta "
"bilaketa gaitasun ahaltsuak ditu."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kaddressbook.appdata.xml:16
msgid ""
"Duplicate detection and merging - KAddressBook can find duplicated contacts "
"from multiple sources and can merge them into a single contact."
msgstr ""
"Bikoiztuak antzematea eta bateratzea - KAddressBook sorburu ezberdinetan "
"bikoiztuta dauden kontaktuak aurkitu eta kontaktu bakarrean bateratu ditzake."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kaddressbook.appdata.xml:17
msgid ""
"Good standard support - KAddressBook can import and export from and to "
"nearly every address book standard."
msgstr ""
"Estandarren euskarri ona - KAddressBook-ek ia-ia helbide-liburu estandar "
"guztietatik eta guztietara inportatu eta esportatu dezake."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kaddressbook.appdata.xml:18
msgid ""
"LDAP integration - Can connect to multiple LDAP servers, which can then be "
"used for contact autocompletion when composing emails in KMail."
msgstr ""
"LDAP integrazioa - LDAP zerbitzari anizkoitzetara konektatu daiteke, ondoren "
"KMail-en e-postak idaztean kontaktuak automatikoki osatzeko erabil "
"daitezkeelarik."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kaddressbook.appdata.xml:19
msgid ""
"Integration - Integrates with other Kontact components, e.g. exporting "
"birthday reminders to KOrganizer"
msgstr ""
"Integrazioa - Kontact-en beste osagai batzuekin integratzen da, adib. "
"KOrganizer-rera urtebetetze oroigarriak esportatuz"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kaddressbook.appdata.xml:20
msgid ""
"QR codes - KAddressBook can display a QR code for each contact to quickly "
"scan it into your phone or send to someone."
msgstr ""
"QR kodeak - KAddressBook-ek kontaktu bakoitzaren QR kode bat azaldu dezake "
"hura zure telefonoarekin azkar eskaneatzeko edo norbaiti bidaltzeko."

#. (itstool) path: screenshot/caption
#: org.kde.kaddressbook.appdata.xml:30
msgid "KAddressBook embedded into Kontact"
msgstr "KAddressBook Kontact-en txertatuta"

